message.body: Great weekend Marky D. Always one of my favorite weekends. Excited for you and Candice. You're going to be an awesome Dad. Love you cuz.

Thanks cuz, really appreciate it, it means a lot. I had a great time too and always great spending time and catching up with u. Thanks for the ride to the airport, hope there wasn't too much traffic. Love you too cuz n send my love to the fam.
